363
00:22:43,680 --> 00:22:49,099
<font color="#90ee90">Free Magic わずかな勇氣</font>
Free Magic 조그마한 용기

364
00:22:49,099 --> 00:22:59,943
<font color="#90ee90">Free Magic あつめて 育ちましょう</font>
Free Magic 모아 자라나자

365
00:23:06,137 --> 00:23:10,416
